5:
I'll be counting on you to cheer me
on!
8:
...For what? We just got here and
have zero context.
12:
Sorry, I got ahead of myself. Take a
look at this!
21: Yep! The prize is the Connubial Ring.
24:
It's one of Mirea's lost relics! Can you
believe it?
29:
Wow, it sure got turned into a
commodity real fast...
33:
Well... I heard that we lost the relics
in the first place because they got
pawned off during difficult times.
Nobody kept track of how many we
lost either.
39: We'll cheer you on. You'll get it back.
44:
That's right! I'll give you the show of
a lifetime too, while I'm at it!
48: No time to waste! Let's go!
53:
Welcome to today's special
competition, sponsored by the
generous Platinum Legends!
54:
Who will be the lucky winner that
walks home with the grand
prize—the Connubial Ring?
57:
...What kind of competition is this? I
just assumed it'd be a grand melee,
but...
61:
The first round is a trivia contest. The
second is an obstacle race. The
third is a duel against a monster...
65:
All of those sound like they're right
up Elmara's alley...
69: Heh. I've got this in the bag!
72:
Question number six! What's the
spiciest menu item available at
Palpebra's most famous pancake
stand?
76:
I know! Blood-red pancakes topped
with liquid acid!
79:
Astonishing! Elmara correctly
answers six questions in a row! Will
she keep her winning streak up?
Only one way to find out! On to the
next round!
87:
With a need for speed, Elmara is the
first to defeat enough monsters to
move on to the final round!
90:
It's the moment you've all been
waiting for! The final round is a
battle royale between our
remaining contestants!
91:
Cross the edge of the stage, and
you're out! Last one remaining is the
victor!
95:
Ohhh, yes! Another chance to show
off these guns!
98:
Alk, Stella—my precious comrades! I
shall obtain this victory and
dedicate it to you!
119:
I am the knight Elmara—and today
you will see why I am known as
Mirea's strongest!
122:
You're not half bad! But you'll have
to do better than that to defeat me—
126:
I'm going to win that ring and
propose to my girlfriend no matter
what!
134:
Argh! You are stronger than I
predicted! What technique!
139:
You want to propose, right? Then
give me everything you got!
141: Rgh... You don't need to tell me that!
145:
Face Mirea's strongest knight with all
your might!
150:
What a turn of events! Elmara's
been knocked off the stage! She's
out!
154:
You showed great resilience and
strength of will. You are worthy of
the ring!
157:
Will everyone in attendance please
offer him a round of glorious
applause?
163:
Are you sure you're fine with things
turning out this way? You just
forfeited a relic...
171:
The Connubial Ring! How come you
have it?
175:
I had a little chat with the winner
and explained the situation. He was
happy to swap his prize out for a
different ring.
177:
What he cared most about was
winning and using the occasion to
propose—not the ring itself!
180:
Nobody around here cares that it's a
sacred relic of a kingdom, huh...
184:
What's a dusty old relic compared
to the fiery hot passion of winning a
competition and proposing?
187:
I, for one, am happy with the way
things turned out! It was a great
performance!
192: You were very cool out there.
196:
Everything worked out! Well, except
for my exercise for the day, but that
can be fixed pretty easily...
200:
Oh! How about we head to the
Kaleidoscope right now?
204:
Huh? You sure you shouldn't take a
breather?
208:
Nope, I'm gonna explode if I sit
around doing nothing! Or do you not
want to go together?
216:
Fine by me, then. Honestly, I kinda
saw this coming.
221:
That's just who I am—changing my
mind on a whim...
225:
And never letting anything get in the
way of my fun!
